    "chat_id": "id_000001",
    "from_id": "id_000002",
    "text": "Shipmates: 2026 Truxtun reunion is set for Fri Oct 2 - Sun Oct 4, Norfolk VA. Hotel block at the Sheraton Waterside, rate held until Sep 1. RSVP to me by Aug 15 for the Saturday dinner headcount.",
    "date": "2026-05-11T16:20:00-04:00",
    "reply_to_message_id": "0"
  },
  {
    "message_id": "1000004",
    "chat_id": "id_000001",
    "from_id": "id_000001",
    "text": "Count me and Doris in. Juan Hernandez will be riding down with me — he's the fellow who's been helping me keep the dates straight.",
    "date": "2026-05-11T17:05:00-04:00",
    "reply_to_message_id": "1000003"
  },
  {
    "message_id": "1000005",
    "chat_id": "id_000001",
    "from_id": "id_000000",
    "text": "Thanks Ray. Penciling in Oct 2-4 and the Aug 15 RSVP deadline. Is the Saturday dinner the same room as last time?",
    "date": "2026-05-11T18:12:00-04:00",
    "reply_to_message_id": "1000003"
  },
  {
    "message_id": "1000006",
    "chat_id": "id_000001",
    "from_id": "id_000002",
    "text": "Same waterside room, Juan. Doors at 1800, memorial roll-call before the meal. Estelle is handling the roll-call list.",
    "date": "2026-05-11T18:40:00-04:00",
    "reply_to_message_id": "1000005"
  },
